title: Ep. #35 | Top Kpop Songs of the 2010s // Theme of the Week
description:
Ready for the biggest K-Pop review of the year?

Thanks to YOUR helpful input, Eric was able to curate a list of the top K-Pop songs from the past decade. Let’s reflect on the best of the best from artists like 2NE1, SNSD, Big Bang, Hyuna, Psy, and many more!

Also, listen to Eric ramble about his life during the release of these classics. What was life like before Spotify, Youtube, and the internet?!

Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.

Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios

Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at http://www.divestudios.io/daebakshow !

#EricNam #DaebakShow #Kpop #2NE1 #SNSD #BigBang #Hyuna #PSY #B2ST
